<br>
Tests for `($funcCheckExists:)` macro, which takes (1) a datamap and (2) the name of a key that may or may not exists --> outputs the value of that key if it exists. Otherwise outputs nothing:
<li>sickTeacher quest: ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's quests, "sickTeacher", "")
<li>Ginger: ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's inv, "ginger", 0)
<li>vigorous attribute: ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's att, "vigorous", 0)